msgstr "選定後端的選用引數（以空格分隔）。"

msgid "ACP agent name"
msgstr "ACP 代理名稱"

msgid ""
"Agent name on the ACP server (e.g. hermes). Empty = auto-discover first "
"agent."
msgstr "ACP 伺服器上的代理名稱（例如 hermes）。留空 = 自動發現第一個代理。"

msgid "Calc spreadsheet tools"
msgstr "Calc 試算表工具"

msgid "Max Rows Display"
msgstr "最大顯示行數"

msgid "Sidebar"
msgstr "側邊欄"

msgid "Max Tool Rounds"
msgstr "最大工具輪次"

msgid "Document Context Strategy"
msgstr "文件上下文策略"

msgid "How much document content to include in LLM context"
msgstr "在 LLM 上下文中包含多少文件內容"

msgid "Auto (by document size)"
msgstr "自動（依文件大小）"

msgid "Full document text"
msgstr "完整文件文字"

msgid "Pages around cursor"
msgstr "游標周圍頁面"

msgid "Outline + excerpt"
msgstr "大綱 + 摘錄"

msgid "Stats + outline only"
msgstr "統計 + 僅大綱"

msgid "Extend max tokens"
msgstr "擴充最大 Token 數"

msgid "Edit extra tokens"
msgstr "編輯額外 Token"

msgid "Extra tokens beyond original text length. 0 = same length as original."
msgstr "超出原始文字長度的額外 token。0 = 與原始長度相同。"

msgid "Web Research Cache"
msgstr "網頁研究快取"

msgid ""
"Cache completed web research reports by normalized query (uses web cache "
"database)."
msgstr "依標準化查詢快取已完成的網路研究報告 (使用網路快取資料庫)。"

msgid "Prompt for Web Research"
msgstr "網路研究提示詞"

msgid "Ask for confirmation before sending a web search query"
msgstr "發送網路搜尋查詢前要求確認"

msgid "Web Research Browser"
msgstr "網頁研究瀏覽器"

msgid ""
"Select the browser backend to use for webpage visits during research (Off "
"uses static HTTP requests)."
msgstr "選擇研究期間用於瀏覽網頁的瀏覽器後端（「關閉」則使用靜態 HTTP 請求）。"

msgid "Off (Static HTTP)"
msgstr "關閉（靜態 HTTP）"

msgid "Firefox (CDP)"
msgstr "Firefox (CDP)"

msgid "Chromium (CDP)"
msgstr "Chromium (CDP)"

msgid "Chrome (CDP)"
msgstr "Chrome (CDP)"

msgid "Cache max (MB)"
msgstr "快取上限 (MB)"

msgid "Max disk size for web search cache (0 to disable)"
msgstr "網頁搜尋快取的最大磁碟大小 (0 以停用)"

msgid "Cache validity (days)"
msgstr "快取有效期限（天）"

msgid "How many days cache entries should be considered valid."
msgstr "快取項目應視為有效的天數。"

msgid "Rich Text Control Sidebar"
msgstr "RTF 控制項側邊欄"

msgid "Formatted chat via RichTextControl. Requires restart."
msgstr "透過 RichTextControl 進行格式化對話。需要重新啟動。"

msgid "Humanizer skill (natural prose)"
msgstr "擬人化技能（自然散文）"

msgid ""
"When enabled, injects guidance into the system prompt so the model makes "
"generated or revised document text sound more natural and human (removes AI "
"slop patterns). Edit the rules in your LibreOffice profile under writeragent/"
"skills/humanizer/SKILL.md (the file is auto-created on first use). A "
"dedicated Skills tab can be added later."
msgstr ""
"啟用後，將引導指令注入系統提示詞，使模型生成或修訂的文件內容聽起來更自然、更"
"像人類（移除 AI 冗贅模式）。請在您的 LibreOffice 設定檔中的 writeragent/"
"skills/humanizer/SKILL.md 編輯規則（該檔案會在首次使用時自動建立）。未來可新"
"增專屬的「技能」頁籤。"

msgid "Doc"
msgstr "文件"

msgid "Enable AI grammar checker (Writer)"
msgstr "啟用 AI 文法檢查器 (Writer)"

msgid ""
"When on, WriterAgent registers its AI grammar proofreader with Linguistic; "
"checked text uses your API (Tools → Options → AI). Underlines appear shortly "
"after you pause typing. Off by default."
msgstr ""
"啟用時，WriterAgent 會將其 AI 文法校對器註冊至 Linguistic；檢查的文字會使用您"
"的 API (工具 → 選項 → AI)。在您暫停輸入後不久，會出現底線。預設關閉。"

msgid "Model (optional)"
msgstr "模型 (選填)"

msgid "Leave empty to use the same text model as chat."
msgstr "留空以使用與聊天相同的文字模型。"

msgid "Pause grammar while chat/agent runs"
msgstr "聊天/代理運行時暫停語法檢查"

msgid ""
"When on, AI grammar skips background requests while sidebar chat or agent "
"runs, to avoid concurrent API calls."
msgstr ""
"啟用時，AI 語法檢查會在側邊欄聊天或代理運行期間跳過背景請求，以避免並發 API "
"呼叫。"

msgid "Batch sentences"
msgstr "批次句子"

msgid ""
"Number of sentences to send per LLM request (1-8). 1 (default) is most "
"reliable; higher values are faster and cheaper but may hit token limits or "
"cause model errors."
msgstr ""
"每次 LLM 請求發送的語句數量 (1-8)。1 (預設值) 最為穩定；較高的數值速度較快且"
"成本較低，但可能會達到 Token 上限或導致模型錯誤。"

msgid "Concurrent requests"
msgstr "並行請求"

msgid ""
"Max simultaneous background grammar API calls (1-8). 1 matches prior "
"behavior. Raise for OpenRouter or other providers that allow parallel "
"requests; use with care alongside sidebar chat."
msgstr ""
"背景語法 API 的最大同時呼叫數 (1-8)。1 為先前行為。若使用 OpenRouter 或其他允"
"許平行請求的提供者可調高此數值；與側邊欄聊天功能同時使用時請謹慎調整。"

msgid "Sentence language detection"
msgstr "句子語言偵測"

msgid ""
"Verify each complete sentence's language against the document locale. AI "
"uses your grammar/chat API; Local uses bundled langdetect (no API call, no "
"venv). Mismatches update CharLocale and re-check grammar."
msgstr ""
"根據文件語言驗證每個完整句子的語言。AI 使用您的語法/聊天 API；Local 使用內建"
"的 langdetect（無 API 呼叫，無需虛擬環境）。若不匹配，將更新字元語言設定 "
"(CharLocale) 並重新檢查語法。"

msgid "Off"
msgstr "關閉"

msgid "AI (LLM)"
msgstr "AI (LLM)"

msgid "Local (langdetect)"
msgstr "本機 (langdetect)"

msgid "Enter key sends sidebar chat message"
msgstr "按下 Enter 鍵發送側邊欄聊天訊息"

msgid ""
"When on, Enter in the sidebar query runs the same action as Send; "
"Shift+Enter inserts a newline. When off, Enter inserts a newline."
msgstr ""
"開啟時，在側邊欄查詢中按下 Enter 鍵會執行與「發送」相同的動作；Shift+Enter 則"
"會插入換行符號。關閉時，Enter 鍵僅插入換行符號。"

msgid "Agent edit review"
msgstr "Agent 編輯審閱"

msgid ""
"Off = direct edits. Record = tracked changes you accept/reject yourself. "
"Wait = apply_document_content blocks (on chat/MCP worker thread) until you "
"review."
msgstr ""
"關閉 = 直接編輯。記錄 = 您自行接受/拒絕的追蹤修訂。等待 = "
"apply_document_content 會封鎖（在聊天/MCP 工作執行緒上），直到您審閱為止。"

msgid "Record (track changes)"
msgstr "記錄（追蹤修訂）"

msgid "Wait for review"
msgstr "等待審閱"

msgid "Draw and Impress tools"
msgstr "Draw 和 Impress 工具"

msgid "Vector Search"
msgstr "向量搜尋"

msgid "Cross-file search"
msgstr "跨檔案搜尋"

msgid ""
"Indexed semantic + keyword search for document_research (corpus.db). "
"Requires embeddings venv — see Python Test."
msgstr ""
"用於 document_research (corpus.db) 的索引語意 + 關鍵字搜尋。需要 embeddings "
"venv — 請參閱 Python 測試。"

msgid "Embeddings + FTS"
msgstr "嵌入 + FTS"

msgid "LlamaIndex"
msgstr "LlamaIndex"

msgid "Zvec (experimental)"
msgstr "Zvec（實驗性）"

msgid "ChromaDB"
msgstr "ChromaDB"

msgid "LanceDB (experimental)"
msgstr "LanceDB (實驗性)"

msgid "Embedding Model"
msgstr "嵌入模型"

msgid "HuggingFace model ID for local provider, or endpoint-specific model ID"
msgstr "用於本地提供者的 HuggingFace 模型 ID，或特定端點的模型 ID"

msgid "Enable cross-file rerank"
msgstr "啟用跨檔案重新排序 (rerank)"

msgid ""
"Second-stage cross-encoder after hybrid retrieve (Embeddings + FTS and "
"LlamaIndex). Off by default."
msgstr ""
"在混合檢索（嵌入 + FTS 與 LlamaIndex）後的第二階段交叉編碼器。預設為關閉。"

msgid "Rerank model"
msgstr "重新排序模型"

msgid ""
"Used only when rerank is enabled. English MiniLM is fast; bge-reranker-v2-m3 "
"is multilingual and downloads ~2.3 GB."
msgstr ""
"僅在啟用重新排序時使用。英文 MiniLM 速度較快；bge-reranker-v2-m3 支援多語言，"
"下載大小約 2.3 GB。"

msgid "cross-encoder/ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2"
msgstr "cross-encoder/ms-marco-MiniLM-L-6-v2"

msgid "BAAI/bge-reranker-v2-m3"
msgstr "BAAI/bge-reranker-v2-m3"

msgid "Core services (config, events, logging)"
msgstr "核心服務 (設定、事件、日誌)"

msgid "MCP"
msgstr "MCP"

msgid "Enable MCP Server"
msgstr "啟用 MCP 伺服器"

msgid ""
"Localhost only, no auth. Clients use http://localhost:<port>/mcp (streamable "
"HTTP)."
msgstr ""
"僅限本機，無需驗證。用戶端使用 http://localhost:<port>/mcp (可串流 HTTP)。"

msgid "MCP Port"
msgstr "MCP 連接埠"

msgid "Python"
msgstr "Python"

msgid "Python venv path"
msgstr "Python venv 路徑"

msgid ""
"If set, runs tools in that venv (bin/python or Scripts/python.exe). If "
"empty, run_venv_python_script uses this process's sys.executable (basic "
"stdlib); use a venv for numpy/pandas and Vision Helpers (paddleocr, "
"paddlepaddle)."
msgstr ""
"若已設定，將在該虛擬環境 (venv) 中執行工具 (bin/python 或 Scripts/"
"python.exe)。若留空，run_venv_python_script 將使用此處理序的 sys.executable "
"(基礎標準函式庫)；請針對 numpy/pandas 與視覺輔助程式 (paddleocr, "
"paddlepaddle) 使用虛擬環境。"

msgid "Test"
msgstr "測試"

msgid "Python script timeout (seconds)"
msgstr "Python 指令碼逾時（秒）"

msgid ""
"Wall-clock limit for Run Python Script, =PYTHON(), and "
"run_venv_python_script."
msgstr ""
"執行 Python 指令碼、=PYTHON() 及 run_venv_python_script 的實際執行時間限制。"

msgid "Max Calc data cells"
msgstr "Calc 資料儲存格上限"

msgid ""
"Maximum cells in =PYTHON() data or Run Python Script data/data_range. Larger "
"values use more RAM and time; UNO range read still dominates."
msgstr ""
"=PYTHON() 資料或執行 Python 指令碼資料/資料範圍 (data/data_range) 的最大儲存"
"格數。較大的數值會消耗更多記憶體與時間；UNO 範圍讀取仍是主要的效能瓶頸。"

msgid "Python session mode"
msgstr "Python 工作階段模式"

msgid ""
"Isolated: each =PYTHON() cell gets a fresh namespace. Shared: one namespace "
"per workbook (variables carry between cells)."
msgstr ""
"隔離模式：每個 =PYTHON() 儲存格皆擁有獨立的命名空間。共用模式：每個活頁簿共用"
"一個命名空間（變數可在儲存格間傳遞）。"

msgid "Isolated (default)"
msgstr "隔離模式（預設）"

msgid "Shared kernel"
msgstr "共用核心"

msgid "Vision / OCR"
msgstr "視覺 / OCR"

msgid "Image scale"
msgstr "影像縮放"

msgid "Upscale before OCR/layout. Try 2.0 for small screenshots."
msgstr "在 OCR/版面分析前進行放大。若為小型螢幕截圖，請嘗試 2.0。"

msgid "Worker timeout (seconds)"
msgstr "背景工作逾時 (秒)"

msgid "Host subprocess limit for Vision Helpers (first model download)."
msgstr "Vision Helpers 的主機子處理序限制 (首次下載模型時)。"

msgid "Docling artifacts path"
msgstr "Docling 產出物路徑"

msgid "Optional folder from docling-tools models download (offline use)."
msgstr "docling-tools 模型下載的可選資料夾（離線使用）。"

msgid "OCR confidence threshold"
msgstr "OCR 信心閾值"

msgid "RapidOCR minimum text score. Raise to reduce garbage text."
msgstr "RapidOCR 最低文字分數。提高此值可減少雜訊文字。"

msgid "OCR entire image"
msgstr "OCR 整張影像"

msgid "Recommended for embedded graphics exported from LibreOffice."
msgstr "建議用於從 LibreOffice 匯出的嵌入式圖形。"

msgid "Table extraction mode"
msgstr "表格擷取模式"

msgid "Accurate (default)"
msgstr "精確 (預設)"

msgid "Fast"
msgstr "快速"

msgid "Table cell matching"
msgstr "表格儲存格比對"

msgid "Align detected table cells with content (extract_structure)."
msgstr "將偵測到的表格儲存格與內容對齊 (extract_structure)。"

msgid "Keep orphan text clusters"
msgstr "保留孤立文字叢集"

msgid "Group unassigned text into clusters for messy layouts."
msgstr "將未指派的文字分組為叢集，以處理雜亂的版面配置。"

msgid "Document insert mode"
msgstr "文件插入模式"

msgid ""
"html = Docling HTML import (default). structured = bbox column layout in "
"Writer; native Calc cells for extract_structure tables."
msgstr ""
"html = Docling HTML 匯入（預設）。structured = Writer 中的 bbox 欄位配置；用"
"於 extract_structure 表格的原生 Calc 儲存格。"

msgid "Standard HTML"
msgstr "標準 HTML"

msgid "Structured (layout / cell grid)"
msgstr "結構化（配置 / 儲存格網格）"

msgid "Layout model"
msgstr "版面配置模型"

msgid "Heron (default)"
msgstr "Heron (預設)"

msgid "Egret large (slower"
msgstr "Egret large (較慢"

msgid "Extract formulas (LaTeX)"
msgstr "擷取公式 (LaTeX)"

msgid "Opt-in. Downloads extra VLM models on first use; slower."
msgstr "選擇加入。首次使用時會下載額外的 VLM 模型；速度較慢。"

msgid "Code block enrichment"
msgstr "程式碼區塊增強"

msgid "Specialized OCR for code/terminal screenshots."
msgstr "針對程式碼/終端機截圖的專用 OCR。"

msgid "Docling document timeout (s)"
msgstr "Docling 文件逾時時間 (秒)"

msgid "Per-conversion timeout inside Docling. 0 = no limit."
msgstr "Docling 內部每次轉換的逾時時間。0 = 無限制。"
